  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "• Comparative analysis of Water Use Master Planning(WUMP) process, Village Development Periodic Planning (VDPP) process and Local Adaptation Plan for Action (LAPA)\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\tPh.D Thesis on water governance\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\tThree Masters Thesis  (Conflict in water Use, Local Planning process, Relationship of poverty and resources)\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t•  Water Use Master Plan process in 4 VDCs by integrating adaptation priorities from VDPP and LAPA ( Helambu, Mahankal, Kiwool and Ichowk VDCs of Sindhupalchowk district)\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t• Guidelines for prioritizing adaptation for climate change in WUMP process\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t•  Climate change and water governance adaptation strategy of the VDC"
    },
    "ne": null
  },
